The paper discusses the economic aspects of ransomware, including pricing strategies and their impact on success. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), economics (cs.EC), and cybercrime (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper may also fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it discusses the likelihood of different schemes being implemented and becoming successful in existing malware.
